  <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
    <h3>Key Benefits by Split</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Hybrid Split:</strong> Combines different training methodologies, good for overall balance and variety</li>
      <li><strong>Full Body Split:</strong> Highest frequency, great for beginners and those with limited training days</li>
      <li><strong>Upper-Lower Split:</strong> Balanced frequency and volume, excellent for most intermediate lifters</li>
      <li><strong>Push-Pull-Legs:</strong> Higher volume per session, ideal for bodybuilding focus</li>
      <li><strong>Double Muscle Group:</strong> Allows specialized focus on complementary muscles, good for intermediate to advanced</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
